# =============================================================================
# Frigate secrets — EXAMPLE ONLY. Copy to /home/rootuser/frigate_new/secrets/.env on the
# server and fill in real values. NEVER commit the real .env to git.
#
# Variable naming: FRIGATE_<INSTANCE>_<SOURCE>_{USER,PASSWORD,HOST}
#   <SOURCE> is a credential/host group defined in inventory/cameras/<inst>.yml.
#   HOST is the camera/DVR IP or hostname (kept out of git on purpose).
#
# Regenerate the authoritative list at any time with:
#   python3 scripts/render.py && cat generated/required-env.txt
# =============================================================================

# ------------------------------- cafe ----------------------------------------
